'''"Snortle"''' is a [[slang]] term used when a particulary pretty girl exhibits this characteristc when laughing. That being defined by a hearty laugh that is punctuated by a snort on the inhale. The result being embarrassment for the girl (very prominent in mixed company) for exhibiting behavior that would be considered un-ladylike, more-over, ironic.

'''Statement'''

"Brooke looked quite elegant in her gown until she snortled and champagne came out of her nose."

'''Origin'''
The base of the term is from [http://72.14.203.104/search?q=cache:Pjgn8VfFiX8J:www3.merriam-webster.com/opendictionary/newword_display_cat.php%3Fcat%3Dstyle%26last%3D30+snortle&hl=en&gl=us&ct=clnk&cd=32//snortle (verb)] as defined by the Merriam-Webster open dictionary. Basically a combination of Chortle and Snort. Although used sparingly in literature, it has become part of the lexicon of [http://www.techdictionary.com/chat.html chat room descriptors] that are used to describe physical actions to the person they are communicating with. The most common form is by a female to describe a personal reaction of extreme laughter to the point of embarrassment.  

